{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Line Varoma tray with baking paper, leaving holes for steam to circulate, and set aside.","Place stock cube in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket, weigh rice in, add water over rice to wet it, then cook <nobr>12 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Place Varoma into position. Weigh broccoli into Varoma dish. Place salmon fillets on prepared Varoma tray, then add salt, pepper, lemon juice and peel. Insert Varoma tray, cover and steam <nobr>16 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Set Varoma aside. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula. Empty mixing bowl, reserving steaming liquid.","Place 200 g steaming liquid (top up with water if needed), milk, flour, butter and ½ tsp salt then cook <nobr>4 min\/100°C\/\/speed 3<\/nobr>.","Add dill and chop <nobr>3 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>.","Serve fish, rice and vegetables with sauce and dill garnish."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1 vegetable stock cube (for 0.5 l)","180 g wild rice","1200 g water","500 g broccoli florets","600 - 800 g fresh salmon fillets","¾ tsp fine sea salt","¼ tsp ground black pepper","1 lemon, zest and juice","200 g milk","30 g plain flour","30 g butter","1 bunch fresh dill (5-10 g) plus 4 sprigs for garnish"]}],"id":"r86034","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-Vm00MK75ySs\/XZVQ6tCMfgI\/AAAAAAAAdHY\/V3e1F7jGNBY13SfaNxlbW56kEctjF1tawCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0__lno76Kb2SLUSPEB.png","title":"Salmon with Broccoli, Rice and Dill Sauce","publishedAt":"2015-05-13T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"43.8 g","fat":"19.5 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"44.9 g","calories":"2217 kJ \/ 530 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking paper","hintsAndTricks":["<strong>Wine Sauce<\/strong>: Replace 50 - 100 g steaming liquid with white wine."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","4 portions"]}